{"tid":42781,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"轉行做物業管理真係咁難？","createTime":"2016-12-17T03:57:42.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-25T15:13:42.000Z","uid":39019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bfe29ec7afcc0a2ef211d8110744221e9dd2894c","tid":42781,"uid":39019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T03:57:42.000Z","msg":"是咁的  我做左3年飲食 做到灰灰地<br />\n於是裸辭  想轉行做物管<br />\n<br />\n上Recruit搵下管業助理  至少sd左CV俾7間公司<br />\n見工既得2間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第一間見完工無通知  第二間叫我等消息second in<br />\n<br />\n我見好多公司都請人<br />\n係咪我無經驗就唔請<br />\n啲仆街HR就覺得我做左幾年餐飲 應該繼續做落去<br />\n好似唔撚俾人轉行咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n初入行做物管咪即係保安+客戶服務<br />\n乜真係咁難入行咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a83db7e88142bb759dff1a58d4e99e78a3f94b2","tid":42781,"uid":21992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T11:39:14.000Z","msg":"咩學歷"},{"pid":"9bdf943a5e87c6b26f647525dc592cd59431e014","tid":42781,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T11:42:33.000Z","msg":"物業管理係資產管理之中最高級既行業<br />\n至少考返個CFA再講"},{"pid":"bbf6b15d8aacfe8ce6ea490247a35a4359a4ad96","tid":42781,"uid":39019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T11:54:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩學歷</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nIVE仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a4534352db07f70566499e42557345be5c10cfb","tid":42781,"uid":39019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T12:20:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>物業管理係資產管理之中最高級既行業<br />\n至少考返個CFA再講</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n客服+保安都要CFA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e2b44f9d0fa28dbc780bed3a303f1eeea80c910","tid":42781,"uid":52,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17